263
00:13:49,270 --> 00:13:50,230
Sir, what are you doing?

264
00:13:50,350 --> 00:13:50,790
Sir,

265
00:13:51,350 --> 00:13:52,030
Sir,

266
00:13:52,150 --> 00:13:52,790
Get away!

267
00:13:52,870 --> 00:13:54,390
Sir, what are you doing, Sir?

268
00:13:55,670 --> 00:13:56,510
